<body>
    <h1>T10 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"8fe3ae358aba" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument=
-1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"d92d5e30f977" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purp=
ose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7f1303a1c9e1">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for creating a <strong>custom AWS CloudWatch dashboard</strong=
> to monitor multiple Amazon EC2 instances.</p>
<p local-id=3D"315a30bd2ffd">The dashboard will provide a centralized monit=
oring interface that displays key infrastructure metrics such as CPU utiliz=
ation, memory usage, disk usage, and network activity.</p>
<p local-id=3D"db4c8ddc4e84">The intended audience for this document includ=
es:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ef90756f632">
<li local-id=3D"19e0105544ec">
<p local-id=3D"c84714c59a0c">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"999def5a054a">
<p local-id=3D"b79623d8d5cf">System Administrators</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e06aad01d4b">
<p local-id=3D"f4ee9827a551">Cloud Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37576a1e16dd">
<p local-id=3D"efe3c2517bdc">Operations Team</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bfbec6f510c9">
<p local-id=3D"03ab5db182f5">Project Managers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9bded9f11959">This document serves as a guideline for design=
ing and implementing the monitoring solution.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"8fe8cd77c489">
<h2 local-id=3D"ef53095c53ce" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scop=
e">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a2f5268e5dcb">The scope of this project is to design and imp=
lement a <strong>custom CloudWatch dashboard</strong> that monitors four EC=
2 instances running within the AWS environment.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1711c21cacfd">The dashboard will include the following metri=
cs:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"40450eac0be1">
<li local-id=3D"5d979801bb0e">
<p local-id=3D"85a1381ed2b1">CPU Utilization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"34f0f7d3f080">
<p local-id=3D"d15aed87b622">Memory Usage (via CloudWatch Agent)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e7b244b35fe">
<p local-id=3D"b1664b627a45">Disk Usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce6a819cb33a">
<p local-id=3D"226c10c8cc9f">Network In</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c448c4f377ae">
<p local-id=3D"0e8b4e74d5df">Network Out</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4bc2ec74892c">The dashboard will use different visualization=
 formats such as:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7a33459c9713">
<li local-id=3D"a520374b6230">
<p local-id=3D"14940ba12aa1">Line charts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cde09fbbb942">
<p local-id=3D"fd4221b63c58">Pie charts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc52d3c73eb1">
<p local-id=3D"4b8623e34ca4">Histograms</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c06fb242357a" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Include=
dinScope">Included in Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8b86d20c9b7f">
<li local-id=3D"abea13c54cb1">
<p local-id=3D"020cc075ef70">Monitoring of 4 EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b016fe41d8ad">
<p local-id=3D"2ab6163b5f49">Dashboard creation in AWS CloudWatch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"306cd51d5541">
<p local-id=3D"5bf53b146097">Visualization of infrastructure metrics</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"9ff833ed2a03">
<p local-id=3D"188e22957f76">Organized dashboard layout</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c5a647f2e1b6" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-NotIncl=
udedinScope">Not Included in Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"735fa5f5a924">
<li local-id=3D"aea912782d31">
<p local-id=3D"fc24c4e6a895">Automated alerting systems</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"40a19c517ac7">
<p local-id=3D"dbcaa428a4fc">Auto scaling configurations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86ab6ae094c2">
<p local-id=3D"0ef828964960">Advanced log analytics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6586b3ec8df">
<p local-id=3D"d1daa145138b">Cost monitoring</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"55854d12af30">
<h2 local-id=3D"355bb0ce67bd" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.3Defi=
nitions,Acronyms,andAbbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviat=
ions</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0c=
40b72c-42a1-46ea-b219-a417569a1951" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5847236fef97">
