<p local-id=3D"a14f0de068e7">DevOps</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"47093fef587d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a51fd53a99d7">Development and Operations</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f5f724f453b2">
<td data-local-id=3D"2611d9d5ec1c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"360f7c19e16e">CPU</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c97eba16429a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6f3ccbbfa021">Central Processing Unit</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cd3b49acd46c">
<td data-local-id=3D"da31dbb1a7cc" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3151db164632">RAM</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9a9ad175247c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ffae950ffb0">Random Access Memory</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d53e7c5c90d5">
<td data-local-id=3D"3f7d27b4e72b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"94debf25b40f">NOC</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"67dc693c0a7a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5ce76656c088">Network Operations Center</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"711aa16ff3d8">
<h2 local-id=3D"a6fc802a4b11" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.4Refe=
rences">1.4 References</h2>
<p local-id=3D"878d7d7a3454">The following resources were used during the p=
reparation of this document:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a44a50146ddc">
<li local-id=3D"07f257832362">
<p local-id=3D"66bdc7ec50ae">AWS Official Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"50fcff59c6c4">
<p local-id=3D"350d3e962d71">AWS CloudWatch User Guide</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ba38d2730a8">
<p local-id=3D"28a17f8b076d">AWS EC2 Monitoring Documentation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f1ea0d831a76">Reference Links:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"267db68eb6d1">
<li local-id=3D"f5e96eb3398b">
<p local-id=3D"76fe5d63eca9"><a href=3D"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cloudwa=
tch" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/c=
loudwatch</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"096991de7686">
<p local-id=3D"3f00cd58334e"><a href=3D"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ec2" cl=
ass=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ec2</a><=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d31c65422eb7">
<h2 local-id=3D"1eb9a31264a3" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Over=
view">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dd23ea3a1600">This document describes the requirements and d=
esign considerations for creating a centralized monitoring dashboard for EC=
2 infrastructure.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8a68a2eccbe5">The document includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bcb4fb09a98c">
<li local-id=3D"87d936594f58">
<p local-id=3D"eaaf98a6779d">Project objectives and business goals</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2d3c454f4ee">
<p local-id=3D"254dfdb6a027">Functional and non-functional requirements</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"a16347a33d0d">
<p local-id=3D"6865b51c4f4f">Use case diagrams and descriptions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"861db72824d3">
<p local-id=3D"8fea7673f959">Risk analysis and mitigation strategies</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e8f5a8b5f2b6">
<p local-id=3D"772df044cacb">Assumptions and dependencies</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"739da6f60fe1">The document serves as a foundation for implem=
enting the monitoring dashboard.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"42fb24c9dfbe">
<h1 local-id=3D"afc1266ca194" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Proje=
ctOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"17dec72fd800" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proj=
ectObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e8c93a8af3dc">The primary objective of this project is to de=
sign and implement a <strong>centralized monitoring dashboard</strong> usin=
g AWS CloudWatch.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e128faf99afa">The system should enable the operations team t=
o:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c044ef47a756">
<li local-id=3D"9ec39293f9b4">
<p local-id=3D"ee7eaca86144">Monitor performance of multiple EC2 instances<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1a5bf8b852a">
<p local-id=3D"f8d52982f511">Quickly identify system issues</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"406ea742a400">
<p local-id=3D"d16f1c6fb10f">Compare infrastructure performance across serv=
ers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6feebf7bc208">
<p local-id=3D"0fb7e5fbbcdc">Improve operational visibility</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2fdbe38333af">
<h2 local-id=3D"e09af2e95fb0" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busi=
nessGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"50bb72ee2a78">The project aims to achieve the following busi=
ness goals:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"17f62b8cce40">
<li local-id=3D"77fd228e9acb">
<p local-id=3D"0b44ae97ce80">Improve infrastructure visibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa4dd2de588f">
<p local-id=3D"8d010c9c2d1b">Reduce time spent monitoring individual instan=
ces</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2abc4b67137f">
<p local-id=3D"f641718ceb65">Detect performance issues quickly</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ac80d48804f">
<p local-id=3D"cd5476804b58">Improve system reliability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d2ee2973280">
<p local-id=3D"0b4c9a02f14e">Provide a centralized monitoring solution</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"90d9f059fab7">
<h2 local-id=3D"d28eed5096de" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Back=
ground">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b45bf97848d5">ABC Technologies operates several EC2 instance=
s for application development and testing.</p>
<p local-id=3D"08e600363bb8">Currently, the operations team monitors each E=
C2 instance individually using the AWS console. This approach is inefficien=
t and does not provide a centralized view of system performance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c4510cc95ddf">To improve operational efficiency, the company=
 requires a <strong>CloudWatch dashboard</strong> that consolidates monitor=
ing metrics for all instances into a single view.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f67d7fc56ab5">This will help the team monitor system health =
more effectively.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"791358815bb6">
<h2 local-id=3D"18cc1a093a96" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Cons=
traints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<p local-id=3D"82cb6fc45ff4">The following constraints may impact the proje=
ct:</p>
<p local-id=3D"c0ea48657d80">Time Constraint<br>
The project must be completed within <strong>3 hours</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ce066518cb9e">Technical Constraint<br>
Memory and disk metrics require the <strong>CloudWatch Agent</strong> to be=
 installed on EC2 instances.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f41c22489387">Access Constraint<br>
Proper AWS permissions are required to create dashboards and view metrics.<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"f003a985bcaf">Resource Constraint<br>
The dashboard will monitor <strong>only four EC2 instances</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b42bc957b61d">
<h1 local-id=3D"2158962e4f84" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Funct=
ionalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"323d13f4bde8" id=3D"T10-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseC=
aseDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"00a767bf283c">The use case diagram represents interactions b=
etween the <strong>DevOps Engineer</strong> and the <strong>CloudWatch moni=
toring system</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"15b25e277565">Main interactions include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b2309e682386">
<li local-id=3D"0e118a3f1f1b">
<p local-id=3D"e39f2f346760">Viewing EC2 performance metrics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc45f730362e">
<p local-id=3D"c7c860e390e8">Monitoring infrastructure health</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5419f8372505">
<p local-id=3D"b0fc126b7d13">Comparing instance performance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d2771638daa">
<p local-id=3D"341bbbe9688f">Identifying abnormal system behavior</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (3)-20260309-183755.png" width=3D=
"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"20c0b03d47d1737c020f0c6840dfb16b17ee1b48dfecb=
daa515c195414cc1c7d" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/do=
wnload/attachments/1837727796/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(3)-20260309-1837=
55.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773081497483&amp;cacheVersion=3D=
1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"432" data-width=3D"928" data-unresolved-comm=
